data.description: Attention first-time homebuyers, downsizers, & savvy investors looking to expand their real estate portfolio. This main floor unit is a gem of convenience. A welcoming atmosphere greets u inside w/a cozy wood-burning fireplace, beautiful flooring, fresh coat of paint, updated bathroom, & stainless steel appliances. Step out onto ur covered patio & bask in the tranquility of the serene retreat. Mthly dues cover water/sewer/garbage, making it an economical choice. More perks include a storage unit & efficient forced air heating. Here's the big advantage - NO rental cap, making this property an enticing prospect. Located in the Kent East Hill area, just moments away from shopping centers, restaurants, schools, & more. A remarkable opportunity.
